2- بسم الله الذي لا يضر مع اسمه شيء في الأرض ولا في السماء وهو السميع العليم "ثلاثا"،
3-رضيت بالله رباً وبالإسلام ديناً وبمحمد ﷺ نبياً "ثلاثاً"،
غفر الله لمن قالها، ونشرها، وبيّض وجهه، وأسقاه من حوض نبيه ﷺ
column4:
لا تنس قبل نومك وصية نبيك ﷺ: 
"إذا أخذت مضجعك فتوضأ وضوءك للصلاة ثم اضطجع على شقك الأيمن، ثم قُل؛
اللهم إني أسلمت وجهي إليك وفوضت أمري إليك وألجأت ظهري إليك رغبة ورهبة إليك لاملجأ ولامنجا منك إلا إليك آمنت بكتابك الذي أنزلت وبنبيك الذي أرسلت".
غفر الله لك،وأسقاك من حوض نبيهﷺ.

column15:
إذا سمعت الأذان،
القِ قلمك، اختم الاجتماع، إنهِ الجلسة،
انتهى الأمر، الله أكبر من كل شيء،
وصلِّ بخشوع فكل ما ينتظرك أقل شأناً من الصلاة،
ونصيبك من الدنيا ينتظرك،
أنت أعطيت الدنيا ساعات فهب لله دقائق.
column16:
قال تعالى:
"وَلَقَدْ بعثنا فِي كُلِّ أُمَّةٍ رَّسُولًا أَنِ اعْبُدُوا الله وَاجْتَنِبُوا الطَّاغُوتَ"،
هذه دعوة الرُسل جميعاً، توحيد الله وحده، وأن لا معبود بحق إلّا هو سُبحانه،
وهذه أعظم المسائل في الحياة وأكبر القضايا، وكل نبي يقول:
" يا قوم اعبدوا الله ما لكم من إله غيره".

column15:
बंगाल में भाजपा ने एक लंबी लड़ाई लड़ी है।

9 साल पहले बंगाल में हमारा वोट % 4 था।

2014 में हमारी सीटें 2 हुई और 18% वोट मिले।

2019 में हमारी सीटें पहुंची 18 पर और 40% वोट मिले।

2021 के चुनाव में भाजपा 200 सीट जीतकर बंगाल में सरकार बनाएगी।

जनसंघ को शुरु के दो राष्ट्रीय अध्यक्ष बंगाल से ही मिले हैं।

पश्चिम बंगाल को भारत के साथ अक्षुण्ण रखने का काम श्यामा प्रसाद मुखर्जी जी ने किया।

column5:

column6: Vacina é um direito de tds e um dever do Estado. O vírus não é de esquerda ou de direita. É um problema da ciência. Não cabe politicagem qdo o assunto é a saúde da população. O Brasil exige um planejamento sério q garanta vacina p/ tds. Só assim vamos resgatar a confiança no país
column7: Nos EUA, 20 milhões de pessoas devem ser vacinadas ainda este ano. E aqui no Brasil, ainda falta o básico: um plano p/ imunização da população com datas, informações transparentes e planejamento.

column11:
.@UNCTAD का प्रतिष्ठित इन्वेस्टमेंट प्रमोशन अवार्ड 2020, @investindia को प्रदान किए जाने पर मैं आदरणीय PM श्री @narendramodi जी को सभी प्रदेशवासियों की ओर से बधाई देता हूं।

column12:
जब देश कोरोना के खिलाफ महत्वपूर्ण लड़ाई को पूरी मजबूती के साथ लड़ रहा है। उस समय विपक्ष द्वारा भोले-भाले किसानों को गुमराह कर कोरोना के विरुद्ध समर को कमजोर करने का कुत्सित प्रयास किया जा रहा है।

आमजन के जीवन और स्वास्थ्य से खिलवाड़ का यह प्रयास कतई स्वीकार्य नहीं होगा।
column13: आज भारत बंद का समर्थन कर अराजकता फैलाने वाले कांग्रेस समेत अनेक दल यह बताएं कि वर्ष 2010-11 के दौरान जिस यूपीए सरकार ने APMC एक्ट में व्यापक संशोधन की वकालत की थी और राज्यों के मुख्यमंत्रियों को इससे संबंधित पत्र लिखे थे, आखिर उस समय उन्होंने यूपीए सरकार का समर्थन क्यों किया था?
column14:
श्री मुलायम सिंह जी ने 2019 में कृषि से संबंधित स्टैंडिंग कमेटी में एपीएमसी मॉडल एक्ट में संशोधन को "किसान हितैषी" बताते हुए उसका समर्थन किया था।

फिर आज यह राजनीतिक दल भारत बंद का समर्थन किस मुंह से कर रहे हैं, इसका जवाब इन्हें देश की जनता को देना होगा।
column15:
मूल्यों व आदर्शों के बगैर राजनीति कभी जन विश्वास का प्रतीक नहीं बन सकती है।

वह सभी राजनीतिक दल, जिन्होंने कृषि संबंधी सुधार के इस महत्वपूर्ण कदम का सत्ता में रहते हुए समर्थन किया था, अपने इलेक्शन मेनिफेस्टो का हिस्सा बनाया था, आज उसका विरोध कर जन विश्वास पर कुठाराघात कर रहे हैं।
column16:
यूपीए सरकार में कांग्रेस व उसके सहयोगी दलों ने किसानों को हमेशा हथियार बनाया लेकिन किसान हित में कोई भी कदम उठाने में सदैव संकोच करते रहे। यह उनके दोहरे चरित्र को दर्शाता है।

यह दल आज भी भोले-भाले किसानों के कंधों पर बंदूक रख कर देश में अराजकता फैलाने का प्रयास कर रहे हैं।
column17:
केंद्र सरकार ने किसानों के हित में कृषि संबंधी सुधारों से जुड़े महत्वपूर्ण विधेयकों के माध्यम से पिछले 06 वर्षों में अनेक क्रांतिकारी कदम उठाए हैं।

किन्तु देश के कुछ राजनीतिक दल भोले-भाले किसानों को भ्रमित कर वातावरण खराब करने का प्रयास कर रहे हैं।

column7:
À venir : Le Braquage de Cayo Perico

Disponible le 15 décembre sur PS4 et en rétrocompatibilité sur PS5.
column8:

column12:
Σύντομα κοντά σας: The Cayo Perico Heist

Στη μεγαλύτερη περιπέτεια του GTA Online ως τώρα, μπορείτε να παίξετε σόλο ή με έως και 3 φίλους σας σε μια νέα εξωτική τοποθεσία.

Διαθέσιμο στις 15/12 για PS4 και με backward compatibility για PS5.
column13:
Již brzy: Vloupačka Cayo Perico

To největší dobrodružství v GTA Online představuje zcela novou, exotickou lokaci pro vloupačku s možností odehrát vše sólo nebo se spojit do týmu až se třemi hráči.

Vyjde 15. prosince na PS4 a díky zpětné kompatibilitě i na PS5.
column14:
Вже скоро: The Cayo Perico Heist

Найбільша пригода в GTA Online відбудеться в екзотичній локації. Попереду зухвале пограбування соло або в змові з трьома іншими гравцями.

Доступно з 15 грудня на PS4 та через зворотну сумісність на PS5
column15:
În curând: jaful de la Cayo Perico

Cea mai mare aventură în GTA Online îți prezintă o locație nouă și exotică de Heist în care poți să joci singur sau împreună cu până la trei prieteni.

Disponibilă de pe 15 decembrie pe PS4 și prin compatibilitate inversă pe PS5
column16:
Hamarosan: The Cayo Perico Heist

Az eddigi legnagyobb GTA Online kaland egy vadonatúj egzotikus rablási helyszínen játszódik, és egyedül vagy akár három másik játékossal játszható.

Elérhető december 15-én PS4-en és PS5-ön visszafelé kompatibilitás révén.
column17:
Çok yakında: Cayo Perico Heist

column11: Malu Gaspar afirma que "o ex-presidente Lula foi procurado para dar entrevista para o livro, mas não quis falar”. Malu diz ainda que “os argumentos da defesa são públicos e foram contemplados ao longo do livro"
column12: A assessoria do ex-presidente Lula disse em nota que Malu Gaspar não ouviu a defesa dele e que repetiu, sem contestação, versões contadas por delatores. Disse também que ela deixou de considerar as provas de inocência obtidas pelos advogados de Lula, e que desmentem os delatores.
column13: A assessoria da Odebrecht disse que a empresa passou por um processo de transformação, e que um monitor do Dep. de justiça dos EUA atestou que o sistema de conformidade da empresa está desenhado e implementado para prevenir e detectar potenciais violações das leis anticorrupção.

column3:
God is going to protect you, heal you, favor you, and take you to the fullness of your destiny.

Be inspired by this message from Joel, "Invisible to the Enemy". Check it out here: https://t.co/KpspxxmnN3 https://t.co/H5hJe30nju
column4: When life tries to push you down, step on you, take your health, squash your dreams, you have to get back up again. Outlast what’s trying to defeat you. The power in you is greater than any power that’s trying to stop you.
column5: God is about to take you higher. Things that have held you back are being broken. New doors are about to open, giants are about to be defeated, talent is about to come out of you that you didn’t know you had.
column6: You may have difficulties now, in your health, your finances, your marriage. You could live worried and panicked. But when you know you’re in a safe place, where God has you hidden, then you can live in peace.
column7:
Victory starts in our minds.

Get a copy of Joel’s NEW book “Empty Out The Negative” for you and a friend here: https://t.co/LJKn1wR4Eh

#EmptyOutTheNegativeBook
#JoelOsteen https://t.co/HFxiP7cMew
column8:
When you honor God, when you stay close to Him, you have an advantage. He hides you when trouble comes. He makes you invisible to the enemy.

Click here to watch, "Invisible to the Enemy": https://t.co/kMfAhXGqHJ https://t.co/DMYDJoz7Af
column9: Enemies may be knocking at your door: debt, trouble, sickness, calamity. Stay in peace; you’re invisible to the enemy. It may show up, but it’s not going to find you.
column10: Faith and fear have something in common. They both ask us to believe something that we can’t see. Whichever one you get in agreement with is the one that’s going to come to pass.
column11: That difficulty is not how your story ends; God has the final say. He’s not only going to take care of what’s trying to stop you, but He’s going to bring you out better.
column12: Trouble is not going to come near you. Why? You’re in the shelter of the Most High. He has you covered. He’s covered your health, covered your marriage, covered your children, covered your finances, covered your dreams.
column13: God can make you invisible to the enemy. Plans that were sent to stop you, strategies designed to keep you from your destiny, cannot stand against our God.
column14: God is your vindicator. He sees what’s happening. If you’ll stay on the high road, He’ll make it up to you.
column15: If you’ll get rid of the bitterness, the offense, the critical spirit, the negativity, you’ll get your passion back; you’ll get that spring in your step. You’ll not only enjoy life more, but you’ll see God’s favor and blessings in new ways.
column16: You have to trust the process. While you’re waiting, things are growing; things are developing. God is bringing it all together.
column17:
God called you an eagle; He created you to soar. Don’t let a sour attitude keep you grounded. It’s time to rise to new levels, to soar to new heights.

Check out "A Fresh New Attitude" on Podcast here! https://t.co/KpspxxmnN3

column3: There’s a teaching moment in every trial that the Almighty sends your way. Each pain makes you stronger; every betrayal makes you wiser, every failure makes you more resilient. He will keep testing us till we learn the intended lesson. Keep learning! Life always has a lesson!
column4: When you’re close to the Almighty, you’ll be extremely grounded. Nothing worldly will shake or affect you that you lose your sense of self. You’ll have inner peace. You won’t be easily provoked. You’re better able to control your anger. You’re calm in the face of adversity!
column5:

In these cold winter months where the temperatures fall subzero lets come together and give warmt…
column6: Wait patiently. It’s never a punishment. It could be a protection. And it’s certainly a preparation for when the door finally opens. It’s all to do with timing. The Lord of the Worlds knows when it’s best to give you what you’ve been asking for day and night!
column7: At times, the Almighty will slow you down just to protect you. A delay doesn’t mean denial. There’s evil ahead of you which you can’t see but He can. So don’t always be in a hurry. Read His signs. You’ll be forever grateful that you didn’t rush headlong into things. Slow down!
column8: Learn to be fair. The Almighty loves those who are just. Sometimes you don’t like someone based on what others have said about him or someone else's description of him. But he turned out to be a good person. So stay away from having preconceived ideas. Give everyone a chance!
column9: RT @wanyanyawalter: Fact : Zimbabweans are awesome people !! @muftimenk Makorokoto  👏🏿👏🏿 https://t.co/L6lQkI62iL
column10: The Almighty will give you what you want when the time’s right. If it’s good for you, He’ll make sure that you get it. If it’s bad for you, He will keep it away from you. Never for a moment think that He hasn’t  heard you. He knows what’s in your heart even before you uttered it!
column11: We often forget who’s in control of our journey. We plan as if everything is guaranteed. As if we’ll get everything we want. But the Almighty has shown us, especially during this pandemic that we should appreciate everything that we have. He can take away anything, anytime!
column12: Learn to wait patiently. Not with a bad attitude. When you see friends being blessed, be happy for them. Pray for their well-being so the Almighty might grant you the same favours. Your turn will come. Live by this principle: when it wasn’t my turn, I never hated. I just waited!
column13: Feel hopeless? Feel like the world is caving in on you? Feel like you’re in total darkness with no light at the end of the tunnel? Remember, no matter what you’re going through, that one sincere prayer can change your entire life. Where there’s hope, there’s life. Always!
column14: The greater the obstacles, the greater the victory. Don’t complain when your test is a difficult one. The Almighty tests those He loves most. He’ll keep testing us. There’s a purpose behind the trial. Tests are a way to purify us. Embrace it. You’ll realize its value eventually!
column15: How you live your life daily matters. Are you sowing seeds of goodness so you can reap them later or are you doing whatever you feel like. Don’t waste your short time in this world. Sow seeds of positivity, gratitude, love, hope etc and see how it impacts those around you.
column16: Almighty. Forgive us for trying to fix things on our own. Forgive us for running around seeking help when we should be turning to You. Forgive us for forgetting how much we need You above everyone & everything else. You know our pain, burden & cares. Heal us. Make us whole again!
column17: Let’s be honest about it. From time to time, we all do foolish things. We make mistakes. As long as we acknowledge our shortcomings and seek forgiveness, nothing we do is beyond the capacity of the Almighty to forgive. Remember, we make mistakes. He doesn’t! He’s perfect!
